It is the entire set of documents that'll be used

3
00:00:10.294 --> 00:00:12.886
for project execution and control.

4
00:00:12.886 --> 00:00:17.172
Now typically, it's going to be the list of tasks you have to go do,

5
00:00:17.172 --> 00:00:21.431
and an estimate, and a schedule, but it'll be a lot more than that,

6
00:00:21.431 --> 00:00:25.886
and we're going to cover all the aspects of what a project plan is,

7
00:00:25.886 --> 00:00:30.386
and also the project the plan is not just the requirements

