and I've divided into two areas, the first are what I call the core elements.

15
00:01:05.886 --> 00:01:11.271
Second are the implementation elements, and within the core elements,

16
00:01:11.271 --> 00:01:12.886
we have three.

17
00:01:12.886 --> 00:01:20.254
We validate our PDD, we build a WBS, or Work Breakdown Structure of tasks,

18
00:01:20.254 --> 00:01:23.261
and we itemize the acceptance criteria,

19
00:01:23.261 --> 00:01:28.886
and I'm going to go into each of these in detail in the following slides.

20
00:01:28.886 --> 00:01:31.833
The second part are the implementation elements,

21
00:01:31.833 --> 00:01:35.623
this is where we apply resources to our WBS,

22
00:01:35.623 --> 00:01:38.486
and we develop estimates for those tasks,

23
00:01:38.486 --> 00:01:40.486
and we develop a schedule,

24
00:01:40.486 --> 00:01:45.732
so this is the core element and what I call the implementation

25
00:01:45.732 --> 00:01:52.501
element of your basic plan for your project.

26
00:01:52.501 --> 00:01:55.886
Okay, let's get started.

