00:01:55.886 --> 00:01:58.750
Step one is to validate the project definition document.

28
00:01:58.750 --> 00:02:03.239
So what you want to do basically is get a team in a room,

29
00:02:03.239 --> 00:02:05.709
you know, all the subject matter experts,

30
00:02:05.709 --> 00:02:07.827
and maybe even some stakeholders, whoever,

31
00:02:07.827 --> 00:02:11.457
and start going through your plan, start looking at it in detail.

32
00:02:11.457 --> 00:02:14.886
So basically what you want to do is you want to validate

33
00:02:14.886 --> 00:02:17.219
the contents that are in your document,

34
00:02:17.219 --> 00:02:21.314
every one of those sections and subsections that we talked about before,

35
00:02:21.314 --> 00:02:26.886
we want to make sure it's still valid and relevant for the project,

36
00:02:26.886 --> 00:02:31.553
and as you go through each one, you might find that oh,

37
00:02:31.553 --> 00:02:34.553
we missed something, we need to update the plan,

38
00:02:34.553 --> 00:02:36.886
